            "pmid": "34231480",
            "title": "Patients with Specific Gastrointestinal Motility Disorders are Commonly Diagnosed as Functional GI Disorders in the Early Stage by Community Physicians due to Lack of Awareness.",
            "abstract": "Data on specific gastrointestinal (GI) motility disorders, such as gastroparesis (GP), chronic intestinal pseudo-obstruction (CIPO), and colonic inertia (CI), as well as awareness among doctors about these disorders are scanty in Asia.",
